        "published_date": "2020-11-18 00:00:00",
        "last_modified_date": "2022-05-17T16:30:54.817Z",
        "post_body": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are pleased to announce that </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cognitiv+ </span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">has been selected as winner of the </span><b>Document Review Solution of the Year </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Award at the 2020 <a href=\"https://legaltechbreakthrough.com/\">LegalTech Breakthrough Awards</a> program.</span></p> \n<!--more-->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are particularly happy because the competition was extremely fierce this year with over <strong>1,250 nominations</strong> coming in from all over the world.</span></p> \n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even more so, as some of the winners from other categories include big players in the legal tech sphere such as Everlaw, K2, LegalZoom, LexisNexis, Notarize, and Sinequa. We are in good company!</span></p> \n<p><b>What is the Legal Tech Breakthrough Award&nbsp;</b></p> \n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The <a href=\"https://legaltechbreakthrough.com/\">LegalTech Breakthrough Awards</a> recognize the top technology companies, solutions and products in the legal technology industry today and is part of the Tech Breakthrough organization. Founded in 2014, Tech Breakthrough creates industry recognition programs for companies ranging from Fortune 500 to early-stage startups in todays most competitive technology sectors.</span></p> \n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The award confirms that 2020 is proving to be a very successful year for <a href=\"/\">Cognitiv+</a>: we have been growing our team (currently recruiting!), chosen to be part of the prestigious <a data-sveltekit-reload href=\"/blog/cognitiv-joins-tech-nation-applied-ai\">TechNation Applied AI program</a> and selected by the UK Department for International Trade to be one of the few Legal Tech companies to join the <strong>3rd Austria Legal Tech Mission</strong>.&nbsp;</span></p> \n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cognitiv+ </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;empowers businesses and law firms with deeper insights on their legal data. Our machine learning technology automatically reviews, identifies, and extracts key provisions from corporate and legal documents. Being awarded the </span><b>Document Review Solution of the Year </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">at the 2020 LegalTech Breakthrough Awards is another recognition of the great work done in an extremely innovative field like <strong>Natural Language Processing, Deep Learning and Vision AI for document review.</strong></span></p> \n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
